snippet.title: 7 Actors Currently ROTTING in Jail (and the Reasons Why)
snippet.description:
Bill Cosby and Michael Jace are some of the actors currently in prison. Tune in to see 7 actors who are currently rotting in jail and the reasons why:

Actors Currently ROTTING In Jail And The Reasons Why
We all hold actors in high esteem and often envy their considerable fame and fortune. What we don’t envy though is the attention and scrutiny they get from every point of the compass whenever they run afoul of the laws of civilization and are hauled off to jail. While it is pretty normal for actors to act up and wind up in jail overnight, what is not normal is their being left to rot in the slammer. Today we will be checking out 7 actors who are currently rotting in jail and detailing what they did to wind up there. Tune in and chill out!

0:00 Introduction
0:05 Bill Cosby
1:47 Michael Jace
2:51 Shannon Richardson
3:54 Harvey Weinstein
5:03 Will Hayden
6:21 Jared Fogle
7:42 Skylar Deleon
